snippet.title: In Space We Brawl - Launch Trailer | PS4, PS3
snippet.description:
In Space We Brawl will storm your local multiplayer gaming nights 
on PS4 and PS3 next week, with a release price of $11.99 and a 20% launch discount for PlayStation Plus subscribers.
